2. Literature review
This section aims to clarify concepts used throughout the paper. As such,
we will focus our attention on the knowledge of the Data Envelopment Analysis
(DEA), focusing on some of its variants, and Artificial Neural Networks (ANN)
approaches, to have deep learning about each one, as well as their specificities
